  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 222.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "While we were marching, of course, everything was light to the-- to the-- to the main street in the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Suddenly, there was a Russian air attack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How do you know it was Russians?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Russians when they bombarded, they first throw-- they call it like Christmas trees, lights, so-- so to see the targets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And apparently, they had a full direct hit on the generator station, and for two minutes all lights went out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was dark, and this guy behind me-- I always used to say, [LAUGHS] years later, it still hurts me-- gave me a [INAUDIBLE] in the tuchus and said, if you don't run, I take it away from you-- run.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for some reason, I said, he's right, and I ran.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I ran all night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I threw away my jacket, and put on the-- the-- the-- the civilian jacket, and scratched again, scratched again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had some-- some old sea pants below my-- my-- my-- my striped pants.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I looked like a civilian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And let me tell you, I wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over 100 people ran away, but the SS had dogs immediately ran after them, and-- and-- and I think maybe who-- guess who else escaped at that time that I found out 30 years later?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- [POINTS] they-- I didn't no about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wear also the same things, and they ran away, and they saved themselves too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But most of them got caught, and shot right in front of everybody to-- to-- to deter the others.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I ran all night, like an animal-- the [? instinct. ?] In the morning, I came to a major [INAUDIBLE], a major street-- a road.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
